{"tid":2170458,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人仲記得小思老師？","createTime":"2020-08-23T09:41:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-23T19:14:35.000Z","uid":142763,"like":42,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"df8e9edb58a295bcf308a1efd6e47316a1d9d31a","tid":2170458,"uid":142763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T09:41:03.000Z","msg":"依家後生一輩（我指嘅係00後），已經唔係好多人認識她。小思老師，即盧瑋鑾教授係香港當代著名散文作家、教育家。亦曾任香港中文大學中文系系主任。她多年來研究香港文學，亦成立「香港文學特藏」及「香港文學資料庫」。<br />\n<br />\n她對教育的熱誠同堅持，令人尊敬。小思老師畢業於新亞書院，師承新儒家大師唐君毅。她亦被譽為新亞精神的傳承者。<br />\n<br />\n要了解她的思想同精神，就要看紀錄片情常在(完整版本，要去大學圖書館睇)同埋她的書。<a href=\"https://youtu.be/cvu5WupZW2s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fcvu5WupZW2s&d=MZ%2BcikgbnzcLbT%2Fpq7%2BWTAoJw9ynFthkhoOYQBA%2BRXM%3D&h=023102a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/cvu5WupZW2s</a><br />\n<br />\np.s. 依家近排好似冇乜人記得她咁，想喺度回緬下佢對香港文學同教育嘅貢獻。"},{"pid":"319376037e3d90f0742146375a1930af124dec0c","tid":2170458,"uid":230146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T09:52:18.000Z","msg":"我好鍾意佢寫嘅嘢"},{"pid":"e048d0bb19a2674cbf1f56a48929ce53ed733a08","tid":2170458,"uid":7332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T09:53:49.000Z","msg":"佔中佢有寫文"},{"pid":"49adf91788e32273b66a12cad78ce00d2a052e5d","tid":2170458,"uid":142763,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"319376037e3d90f0742146375a1930af124dec0c","tid":2170458,"uid":230146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T09:52:18.000Z","msg":"我好鍾意佢寫嘅嘢"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T09:56:50.000Z","msg":"有冇睇香港家書，一生承教？"},{"pid":"de5c1d7b211a9eacde9cea16ae834aedf29cbdd1","tid":2170458,"uid":2795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T09:56:50.000Z","msg":"城大個時有幸聽佢talk<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2d93894f25fe714baf068ddd2d808bd358cada4","tid":2170458,"uid":142763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e048d0bb19